snippet.title: Block Swap Trailer
snippet.description:
Block Swap is a simple but challenging puzzle game. Play through hundreds of levels where you swap blocks to sort levels by colors in as few moves as possible.

Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ClaudioVertemara.BlockSwap
Itch.io: https://cloudyo.itch.io/block-swap
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/block-swap/516223

Music: https://freesound.org/people/joshuaempyre/sounds/251461/
